6 SUBTITLE.
7 (II) “VALUE” INCLUDES THE MARKET VALUE OF ANY PROPERTY
8 DAMAGED IN FURTHERANCE OF THE CRIME AND ANY COSTS TO REPAIR, REPLACE,
9 OR RESTOCK ANY DAMAGED OR STOLEN PROPERTY.
10 (B) A PERSON MAY NOT COMMIT ORGANIZED RETAIL THEFT OF PROPERTY
11 WITH AN AGGREGATE VALUE EXCEEDING $1,500.
