23 OR A FINE NOT EXCEEDING $15,000 OR BOTH; AND
24 (II) SHALL RESTORE THE PROPERTY TAKEN TO THE OWNER OR
25 PAY THE OWNER THE VALUE OF THE PROPERTY OR SERVICES; OR
26 (3) $100,000 OR MORE IS GUILTY OF A FELONY AND:
27 (I) IS SUBJECT TO IMPRISONMENT NOT EXCEEDING 20 YEARS
28 OR A FINE NOT EXCEEDING $25,000 OR BOTH; AND
